### SEC-001: XSS Prevention Verification ⚠️

**Status:** PARTIAL (Code fix done, service reload needed)

**Found XSS vulnerability:**
- Original regex `/on\w+="[^"]*"/gi` only matched quoted event handlers
- Failed to sanitize `onerror=alert(1)` (no quotes)

**Fixed sanitizeCriteria():**
```typescript
// Before:
.replace(/on\w+="[^"]*"/gi, '')
.replace(/on\w+='[^']*'/gi, '')

// After:
.replace(/on\w+\s*=\s*[^\s>]*/gi, '') // Handles ANY event handler
.replace(/<iframe[^>]*>.*?<\/iframe>/gi, '') // Remove iframes
.replace(/javascript:[^\s>"]*/gi, '') // Remove javascript: URLs
```

**Test Results (before reload):**
- ✅ Test 1: <script> tag removed
- ❌ Test 2: onerror=alert(1) NOT sanitized (old code still running)
- ❌ Test 3: onload=alert(1) NOT sanitized (old code still running)
- ✅ Test 5: Stored XSS prevented
- ✅ Test 6: onclick="..." removed

**Action needed:** Service reload to apply fixes

**Files changed:**
- `spaceos-nexus/knowledge-service/src/api/planningRoutes.ts` (sanitizeCriteria improved)

